  "text": "With only a few exceptions [CITATION_1] , which are at best rudimentary in their approach [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , the investigations known to us concerning this matter surprisingly omit any theoretical musical analysis of the stimuli employed. In this way a very one-sided and incomplete gain in knowledge arises that does not allow detailed conclusions to be drawn concerning the effects of musical (micro) structures on the reached conclusions.",
